notes.title: Conflicts of Interest
notes.p: 60P Pharmaceuticals; Eisai Co., Ltd.; Johnson & Johnson; Merck KGaA; MSD; and Pfizer reviewed and approved the descriptions of their WIPO Re:Search collaborations for this article.
